                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6632" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0135</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7801 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">可持续扶贫：中国人寿社会责任与政府公共治理的协同</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Sustainable Poverty Alleviation: Synergy between China Life&#39;s Social Responsibility and Government Public Governance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈志松，张湛澜，丁慧，陈茜</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国人寿保险股份有限公司江苏省分公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公共关系/外事部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">保险扶贫；社会责任；协同治理；精准扶贫；共同富裕</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Insurance-based Poverty Alleviation; Social Responsibility; Synergy Governance; Precise Poverty Alleviation; Common Prosperity</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">十八大以来，习近平总书记从人民群众的利益和幸福的角度出发，提出了“精准扶贫”的战略思想。本案例描述了中国人寿保险股份有限公司江苏省分公司勇担企业社会责任，从建档立卡贫困人口最关心、最需要、最迫切的保险保障着手，解放思想、开拓思路，全力打造出丰富的扶贫保险体系。省分公司从苏北到苏南逐步推进，积极与地方政府协同联动，因地制宜推进各类扶贫保险，例如宿迁“互联网+保险+公益”的“扶贫100”、泰州“126”精准医疗扶贫项目、南通“1+1”扶贫保险等。通过不断地创新产品、深化服务，极大地缓解了贫困人口的经济压力，为群众撑起“保护伞”，完善和深化了保险助推精准扶贫的创新模式，并积极融入乡村振兴，为“三农”发展保驾护航，为实现共同富裕贡献力量。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Since the 18th National Congress, General Secretary Xi Jinping has put forward the strategic idea of “precise poverty alleviation” from the perspective of people&#39;s interests and happiness. This case describes that the Jiangsu Branch of China Life Insurance Co., Ltd. is courageously responsible for corporate social responsibility, starting with the insurance protection that the poor are most concerned about, need and urgently need, emancipate their minds and open up their minds,and make every effort to create a rich poverty alleviation insurance system. The provincial branch has gradually promoted from northern Jiangsu to southern Jiangsu, actively working with local governments to promote all kinds of poverty alleviation insurance according to local conditions. For example, Suqian “Internet + insurance + public welfare” poverty alleviation project, Taizhou “126” precision medical poverty alleviation project, Nantong “1+1” poverty alleviation insurance and so on. By constantly innovating products and deepening services, it has greatly alleviated the economic pressure on the poor, propped up a “protective umbrella” for the masses, improved and deepened the innovative model of insurance to promote accurate poverty alleviation, and actively integrated into the revitalization of rural areas. to protect the development of agriculture, rural areas and farmers, and contribute to the realization of common prosperity.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">保险扶贫内在机理；企业社会责任的概念与内涵；协同治理；精准扶贫；多元协同精准扶贫；贫困恶性循环理论；贫困-疾病恶性循环理论；马克思主义共同富裕思想；保险防贫的作用机理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
